Package: pttR
Title: Retrieve and Process Text Data from PTT
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yongfu", "Liao", email = "liao961120@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("LOPE @ NTU", role = "cph"))
Description: Provide functions to process raw data access through PTT Corpus, 
    including Chinese word segmentation based on a PTT-specific dictionary, 
    corpus object construction, conversion between such corpus objects required 
    by different packages (such as tm and quanteda).
URL: https://liao961120.github.io/pttR/, https://github.com/liao961120/pttR
BugReports: https://github.com/liao961120/pttR/issues
